heh heh<br>
I play a level 35 untwinked paladin, and there are only two things I've seen so far that I would consider getting.  More might pop up later on, but I'm fairly certain that they will only appear on the giant animals that are found in this zone.  Since said animals give Peacekeeper faction hits, and I'm a Peacekeeper, I don't think I'll be taking them down.<br>
Incidentally, the two items are...<br>
1.)  A FS Naginata to replace the bronze one I keep around just for the look.<br>
2.)  The spiritling stones, which are part of a quest involving the Tower of Frozen Shadows.  Unfortunately, the spiritlings are trivial when ToFS becomes doable, and based on this, I've written to Verant about it.<br>
In short, I have yet to see any items I would consider getting based on stats, or anything similar.<br>
